<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Estoque Laborat├│rio - Supabase</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  <!-- Google Fonts: Inter e Fira Mono -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fira+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/xlsx/dist/xlsx.full.min.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

<div id="auth-screen" class="auth-screen">
  <div class="auth-card">
    <div class="auth-hero">
      <div class="auth-kicker">Acesso protegido</div>
      <div class="auth-title">Estoque Laborat├│rio</div>
      <div class="auth-copy">Entre com sua conta para visualizar estoque, hist├│rico e custos. Os dados do sistema ficam bloqueados at├® a autentica├º├úo.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="auth-form" id="login-form">
      <div class="auth-row">
        <div class="modal-label">Usu├írio ou e-mail</div>
        <input type="text" class="modal-input" id="login-user" placeholder="pcp ou usuario@empresa.com" autocomplete="username" autocorrect="off" spellcheck="false">
      </div>
      <div class="auth-row">
        <div class="modal-label">Senha</div>
        <input type="password" class="modal-input" id="login-pass" placeholder="senha" autocomplete="current-password">
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: right; margin-top: -5px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
        <a href="#" id="link-forgot-pass" style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; transition: color 0.15s;">Esqueci minha senha</a>
      </div>
      <label class="auth-check" for="remember-login">
        <input type="checkbox" id="remember-login" checked>
        <span>Manter meu acesso neste navegador</span>
      </label>
      <div class="modal-err" id="login-err"></div>
      <button class="btn-admin auth-submit" id="auth-submit">Entrar</button>
      <div class="auth-hint">Utilize sua conta @selbetti.com.br para acesso administrativo completo.</div>
      <div class="auth-lgpd" style="font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); text-align: center; margin-top: 15px; line-height: 1.4; opacity: 0.85; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 12px;">
        ­ƒöÆ <strong>Aviso de Privacidade (LGPD):</strong> Ao fazer login, coletamos seu e-mail corporativo para fins estritos de auditoria de movimenta├º├úo do estoque e controle interno, em conformidade com as pol├¡ticas de seguran├ºa da informa├º├úo da empresa.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TELA DE RECUPERA├ç├âO DE SENHA (FORGOT PASSWORD) -->
    <div class="auth-form" id="forgot-pass-form" style="display: none;">
      <div style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;">
        Insira seu e-mail corporativo cadastrado para receber um link de redefini├º├úo de senha no seu e-mail.
      </div>
      <div class="auth-row" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
        <div class="modal-label">E-mail corporativo</div>
        <input type="email" class="modal-input" id="forgot-email" placeholder="usuario@selbetti.com.br" autocomplete="email" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
      </div>
      <div class="modal-err" id="forgot-err" style="min-height: 1.2rem; text-align: center; font-weight: 600;"></div>
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-top: 5px;">
        <button class="btn-admin auth-submit" id="forgot-submit" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">Enviar E-mail de Recupera├º├úo</button>
        <button class="btn-cancel" id="forgot-back" style="width: 100%; font-size: 13px; justify-content: center;">Voltar para o Login</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- OVERLAY DE SELE├ç├âO DE AMBIENTE -->
<div id="env-selector-overlay" class="modal-overlay" style="display:none; align-items: center; justify-content: center; z-index: 9999; backdrop-filter: blur(20px); background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);">
  <div class="modal-box" style="width: 760px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 24px; padding: 40px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">
    <div style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 8px;">Bem-vindo ao Sistema</div>
    <h2 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--text);">Escolha o Ambiente Operacional</h2>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 35px; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
      Selecione um contexto operacional abaixo para carregar as abas, dashboards e configura├º├Áes adequadas para suas tarefas.
    </p>
    
    <div id="env-cards-grid" class="env-grid">
      <!-- Cards gerados dinamicamente via JS -->
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="app-shell">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <div class="header-bar">
    <div class="logo-selbetti">selbetti</div>
    <div class="header-center">
      <div class="header-title">CONSULTA DE <span>PE├çAS</span></div>
      <div class="header-subtitle">Consulte o estoque e registre entradas e sa├¡das de componentes</div>
    </div>
    <div class="header-right">
      <div id="sector-switcher" style="display:none; align-items: center; background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 99px; padding: 3px; gap: 2px;">
        <button id="btn-sector-lab" class="sector-btn active" onclick="window.changeSector('LAB')">­ƒö¼ Lab</button>
        <button id="btn-sector-remanu" class="sector-btn" onclick="window.changeSector('REMANU')">ÔÜÖ´©Å Remanufatura</button>
      </div>
      <div id="admin-badge" class="badge-admin-pill" style="display:none">­ƒöÆ Admin</div>
      <div id="custo-real-badge" style="display:none; align-items:center; gap:6px; background:#10b981; color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:4px 10px; border-radius:999px; letter-spacing:0.5px; animation: pulse-badge 2s infinite;">­ƒÆ▓ CUSTO REAL</div>
      <div class="stat-pill"><span class="dot"></span><span id="stat-in-stock">0</span> em estoque</div>
      <div class="stat-pill"><span class="dot red"></span><span id="stat-zero">0</span> zeradas</div>
      <button id="btn-login" class="btn-admin">+ ├ürea Admin</button>
      <button id="btn-reset-gear" class="btn-gear" title="Menu Administrativo" onclick="openAdminMenu()">ÔÜÖ´©Å</button>
      <button id="btn-logout" class="btn-admin logout" style="display:none">Ôå® Sair</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- TABS -->
  <div class="tab-bar">
    <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="dashboard">­ƒôè Dashboard</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="estoque">­ƒôª Estoque</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="historico">­ƒôï Hist├│rico</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="movimentacoes">­ƒôê Movimenta├º├Áes</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="modelo-custo">­ƒÆ░ Custo/Modelo</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="auditoria" id="tab-btn-auditoria" style="display:none">­ƒöì Auditoria</button>
  </div>

  <!-- VIEWS -->
  <div id="view-dashboard" class="view active">
    <div class="dash-scroll">
      <div class="dash-cards">
        <div class="dash-card c-total">
          <div class="dash-card-label">TOTAL DE CADASTROS</div>
          <div class="dash-card-value" id="dash-total">0</div>
          <div class="dash-card-sub">modelos no sistema</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dash-card c-stock">
          <div class="dash-card-label">MODELOS EM ESTOQUE</div>
          <div class="dash-card-value" id="dash-instock">0</div>
          <div class="dash-card-sub">com saldo positivo</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dash-card c-zero">
          <div class="dash-card-label">VOLUME TOTAL (F├ìSICO)</div>
          <div class="dash-card-value" id="dash-vol-total">0</div>
          <div class="dash-card-sub">unidades no laborat├│rio</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dash-card c-low" id="card-low-stock" style="cursor:pointer; transition: transform 0.2s;" onclick="toggleLowStockFilter()">
          <div class="dash-card-label">ESTOQUE CR├ìTICO</div>
          <div class="dash-card-value" id="dash-low-count" style="color:var(--red)">0</div>
          <div class="dash-card-sub">menos de 5 unidades</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dash-section-title">Itens com Saldo em Estoque</div>
      <div class="table-wrap">
        <table class="dash-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Pe├ºa</th>
              <th>C├│digo</th>
              <th style="text-align:center">Quantidade</th>
              <th>Situa├º├úo</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody id="dash-tbody"></tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div id="dash-empty" style="display:none" class="hist-empty">Nenhum item com saldo em estoque.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="view-estoque" class="view">
    <div class="search-area">
      <div class="search-row">
        <input type="text" class="search-input" id="search-main" placeholder="­ƒöì  Buscar por descri├º├úo, c├│digo ou use % para busca m├║ltipla..." autocomplete="off">
      </div>
      <div class="search-tip" id="search-tip"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-bar" id="filter-bar-container">
      <span class="filter-bar-label">FILTROS:</span>
      <span id="brand-chips"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="result-info">
      <span id="result-count">0</span> resultado(s)
      <button class="btn-saida-lote" id="btn-baixa-selb" onclick="openSaidaModal()">Baixa por SELB</button>
    </div>
    <div class="table-wrap">
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>C├│digo</th>
            <th>Descri├º├úo</th>
            <th style="text-align:center">Estoque</th>
            <th style="text-align:right">Valor Unit.</th>
            <th>A├º├Áes</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="result-body"></tbody>
      </table>
      <div class="empty-state" id="empty-state">Nenhum resultado encontrado.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Outras views simplificadas por enquanto -->
  <div id="view-historico" class="view">
    <div class="hist-toolbar" style="margin-bottom: 1.2rem; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); position: relative;">
      <input type="text" class="hist-search" id="hist-search" placeholder="­ƒöì Buscar c├│digo, obs..." autocomplete="off">
      <select class="hist-filter" id="hist-tipo">
        <option value="">Todos os tipos</option>
        <option value="entrada">Entrada</option>
        <option value="sa├¡da">Sa├¡da</option>
      </select>
      <input type="date" class="hist-filter" id="hist-d1" title="Data inicial" style="cursor:pointer">
      <span style="font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--text-muted);flex-shrink:0">at├®</span>
      <input type="date" class="hist-filter" id="hist-d2" title="Data final" style="cursor:pointer">
      <button class="btn-cancel" onclick="document.getElementById('hist-search').value=''; document.getElementById('hist-tipo').value=''; document.getElementById('hist-d1').value=''; document.getElementById('hist-d2').value=''; renderHistorico()" style="padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem; font-size: 0.8rem;">Limpar</button>
      <span class="hist-count" id="hist-count" style="margin-left: auto;">0 registros</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hist-table-wrap">
      <table class="hist-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Data/Hora</th>
            <th>C├│digo</th>
            <th>Tipo</th>
            <th style="text-align:center">Qtd</th>
            <th style="text-align:right">Vlr. Unit.</th>
            <th style="text-align:right">Vlr. Total</th>
            <th>Usu├írio</th>
            <th>SELB / Obs</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="hist-tbody"></tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- VIEW MOVIMENTA├ç├òES -->
  <div id="view-movimentacoes" class="view">
    <div class="mov-container">
      <div class="mov-header">
        <h2>­ƒôê Dashboard de Movimenta├º├úo</h2>
      </div>
      <!-- Filtros -->
      <div class="hist-toolbar" style="margin-bottom: 1.2rem; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); position: relative;">
        <input type="text" class="hist-search" id="mov-prod" placeholder="­ƒöì Filtrar c├│digo ou modelo..." autocomplete="off">
        <select class="hist-filter" id="mov-tipo">
          <option value="">Todos os tipos</option>
          <option value="entrada">Entrada</option>
          <option value="sa├¡da">Sa├¡da</option>
        </select>
        <input type="date" class="hist-filter" id="mov-d1" title="Data inicial" style="cursor:pointer">
        <span style="font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--text-muted);flex-shrink:0">at├®</span>
        <input type="date" class="hist-filter" id="mov-d2" title="Data final" style="cursor:pointer">
        <button class="btn-cancel" onclick="document.getElementById('mov-prod').value=''; document.getElementById('mov-tipo').value=''; document.getElementById('mov-d1').value=''; document.getElementById('mov-d2').value=''; renderMovDashboard()" style="padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem; font-size: 0.8rem;">Limpar</button>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Cards KPI -->
      <div class="dash-cards" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <div class="dash-card c-total">
          <div class="dash-card-label">Total Entradas</div>
          <div class="dash-card-value" id="mov-kpi-entrada">0</div>
          <div class="dash-card-sub" id="mov-kpi-entrada-val">R$ 0,00</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dash-card c-zero">
          <div class="dash-card-label">Total Sa├¡das</div>
          <div class="dash-card-value" style="color:var(--red)" id="mov-kpi-saida">0</div>
          <div class="dash-card-sub" id="mov-kpi-saida-val">R$ 0,00</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dash-card c-stock">
          <div class="dash-card-label">Saldo L├¡quido</div>
          <div class="dash-card-value" id="mov-kpi-saldo">0</div>
          <div class="dash-card-sub">entradas ÔêÆ sa├¡das</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dash-card c-low">
          <div class="dash-card-label">VALOR TOTAL EM ESTOQUE</div>
          <div class="dash-card-value" style="color:var(--blue)" id="mov-kpi-total-vol">0</div>
          <div class="dash-card-sub" id="mov-kpi-total-val">R$ 0,00</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ├ürea dos Gr├íficos -->
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        <div class="card" style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid var(--border); box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">­ƒôë ENTRADA VS. SA├ìDA POR DIA</h4>
          <canvas id="chart-daily" height="180"></canvas>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid var(--border); box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">­ƒôè VOLUME POR SEMANA</h4>
          <canvas id="chart-weekly" height="180"></canvas>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tabela Detalhada por Data -->
      <div class="table-wrap">
        <table class="dash-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Data</th>
              <th style="text-align:center">Entrada (Qtd)</th>
              <th style="text-align:center">Sa├¡da (Qtd)</th>
              <th style="text-align:center">Saldo</th>
              <th style="text-align:right">R$ Entradas</th>
              <th style="text-align:right">R$ Sa├¡das</th>
              <th style="text-align:right">Total (R$)</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody id="mov-tbody"></tbody>
        </table>
        <div class="empty-state" id="mov-empty" style="display:none">Nenhuma movimenta├º├úo para este filtro.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- VIEW REVISADOS -->
  <div id="view-revisados" class="view">
    <div class="mov-container">
      <div class="mov-header">
        <h2>­ƒøá´©Å Registro de SELBs Revisados</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="background: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border);">
        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 15px;">
          ­ƒöº <strong>SELBs Revisados sem Troca de Pe├ºa</strong> (um por linha ou separado por v├¡rgula)
        </p>
        
        <textarea id="revisados-textarea" 
                  placeholder="Ex: A001&#10;B012&#10;C034" 
                  style="width: 100%; height: 150px; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 15px; resize: vertical;"></textarea>
        
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 15px;">
          <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px;">
            <label style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-muted); text-transform: uppercase;">Data da Sa├¡da</label>
            <input type="date" id="revisados-data" style="padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 13px;">
          </div>
          <div style="align-self: flex-end;">
            <button class="btn-admin" onclick="processarRevisados()" style="padding: 10px 25px;">Ô£ö´©Å Confirmar SELBs</button>
          </div>
          <div id="revisados-status" style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; align-self: flex-end; margin-bottom: 8px;"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="margin-top: 20px; background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border);">
        <h4 style="margin: 0 0 15px 0;">­ƒôï ├Ültimos Registros</h4>
        <div class="table-wrap" style="max-height: 300px; overflow-y: auto;">
          <table class="dash-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Data/Hora</th>
                <th>SELB</th>
                <th>Registrado por</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody id="revisados-tbody"></tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- VIEW CUSTO/MODELO (RELAT├ôRIO FINANCEIRO PREMIUM) -->
  <div id="view-modelo-custo" class="view">
    <div class="mov-container">
      <!-- Filtros Estilo BI -->
      <div class="hist-toolbar" style="margin-bottom: 25px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 12px 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; background: white;">
        <div style="position: relative; flex: 1;">
          <input type="text" id="mod-busca" placeholder="­ƒöì Filtrar modelo..." style="width: 100%; padding: 10px 15px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg-hover); font-size: 14px;">
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
          <input type="date" id="mod-d1" style="padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 13px;">
          <span style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted);">at├®</span>
          <input type="date" id="mod-d2" style="padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 13px;">
        </div>
        <button class="btn-cancel" onclick="clearModFilters()" style="padding: 8px 15px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px;">Ô£ò</button>
        <button class="btn-cancel" id="btn-remanu-vinculos" onclick="openVinculosRemanu()" style="display:none; padding: 10px 15px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold;">­ƒöù Vincular Fus├Áes</button>
        <button class="btn-confirm" onclick="renderModeloCusto()" style="padding: 10px 25px; border-radius: 8px;">Gerar Relat├│rio</button>
      </div>

      <!-- Grid de Conte├║do -->
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr; gap: 25px;">
        
        <!-- Coluna da Esquerda: Cards KPI -->
        <div class="mod-kpi-list" id="kpi-container-lab">
          <div class="mod-kpi-item c-atend">
            <div class="mod-kpi-icon">­ƒôá</div>
            <div class="mod-kpi-content">
              <div class="mod-kpi-label" id="mod-kpi-modelos-label">MODELOS ATENDIDOS (0 M├üQUINAS)</div>
              <div class="mod-kpi-value" id="mod-kpi-modelos">0</div>
              <div class="mod-kpi-sub">equipamentos distintos</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mod-kpi-item c-invest">
            <div class="mod-kpi-icon">­ƒÆ░</div>
            <div class="mod-kpi-content">
              <div class="mod-kpi-label">TOTAL INVESTIDO</div>
              <div class="mod-kpi-value" id="mod-kpi-total" style="color: #f97316;">R$ 0,00</div>
              <div class="mod-kpi-sub">custo de pe├ºas em sa├¡das</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mod-kpi-item c-expensive" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick="window.openDetalheModelo('expensive')">
            <div class="mod-kpi-icon">ÔÜá´©Å</div>
            <div class="mod-kpi-content">
              <div class="mod-kpi-label">MODELO MAIS CARO ­ƒöì</div>
              <div class="mod-kpi-value" id="mod-kpi-top" style="font-size: 15px; color: #1e293b;">ÔÇö</div>
              <div class="mod-kpi-sub" id="mod-kpi-top-val" style="font-weight: 700;">R$ 0,00</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mod-kpi-item c-cheap" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick="window.openDetalheModelo('cheap')">
            <div class="mod-kpi-icon">Ô£à</div>
